    public class HistoricTaskWrapper
extends Object
implements Task
    TODO: This class is a hack, to quickly convert a HistoricTaskInstance to a Task, so we can reuse the existing components for a task. Obviously, this is not a good approach in the long run.

    Joram Barrez
